{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"fields":{"description":"## Description\nDocument the new surface so clients can adopt it: the optional `[metrics]` extra + external-CLI prerequisites (scc, jscpd via npx), the `[code_health]` config keys, the analyzer/adapter set, and the hard Unavailable fallback contract.\n\n## Review-driven corrections\n- `tests/scripts/test_metrics_docs.py` ALREADY exists (ticket 121b) asserting a narrower contract — EXTEND it, do not break the existing assertions.\n- Config keys belong in `docs/config.md` (the canonical config design-of-record + reference), in addition to user-guide/reuse-surface.\n- Depends on the FINAL shape from 0734 (recorded edge is the non-blocking relates_to->0734; treat 0734 as the content prerequisite).\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- [ ] docs/reuse-surface.md metrics section: analyzer seam + `[metrics]` extra + external CLIs.\n- [ ] docs/config.md: `[code_health]` keys/types/defaults; docs/user-guide.md Metrics section: tool prereqs + \"no analyzer -> Unavailable\" behavior.\n- [ ] AGENTS.md metrics pointer updated if the one-liner changed.\n- [ ] tests/scripts/test_metrics_docs.py extended (existing assertions still pass).\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] test_metrics_docs.py passes (old + new assertions); docs lint clean.\n\n## Dependencies: 0734 (content prerequisite; relates_to edge recorded).\n## Files likely touched: docs/reuse-surface.md, docs/config.md, docs/user-guide.md, AGENTS.md, tests/scripts/test_metrics_docs.py\n## Estimated scope: M"}},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"EDIT","timestamp":1784523346596937001,"uuid":"c2a25993-9240-4469-82a8-e456290a8587"}